channel.title: Nightz - Maland2016 [EDM, Poppish]
channel.description:
Lead single from M-Sides Part Two, coming soon! This album's only going to be on YouTube because I don't want to risk running out of space on SoundCloud yet (and no I am not deleting tracks, I am that stubborn. :stuck_out_tongue:)
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DSzsuBlYC38
(Fun fact, I was halfway through this and realized it sounded a bit like Owl City. But, that's not a big deal for me, I love Adam's work! Also, no, the lowercase i is not a shoutout to NiGHTS, that's just how the text came.)
